{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1679-06_167","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"Le Printemps d’Olympe","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juin 1679 [tome 6], p. 167-175.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Quoy que nous commencions d’entrer dans l’Eté, vous ne serez pas fâchée que je rappelle les premiers jours de la derniere Saison pour vous faire voir une Piece fort galante de laquelle ils ont fourny la matiere. Vous sçavez, Madame, que tout le mois d’Avril s’est passé en pluyes, &amp; qu’on l’a pû compter cette année pour un mois d’Hyver. C'est là-dessus qu’on a fait ces Vers.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"@type":"head","#1":{"value":"Le Printemps","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"d’Olympe.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"l":[{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[0]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[0]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"BElle Olympe, dont les appas","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[0]/#"}},"Font tant de méchans coups dont on n’ose se plaindre,","Et qui sçavez vous faire aimer &amp; craindre",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[3]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[3]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Par tel qui ne s’en vante pas ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[3]/#"}},"Comme en desirs d’apprendre à vostre âge on abonde,",{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[5]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"N'estes-vous point en peine de sçavoir","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[5]/#"}},"D'où vient que nuit &amp; jour il ne fait que pleuvoir ;","Que le vent qui sans cesse à nos oreilles gronde,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[8]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[8]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Dans la plus belle des saisons","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[8]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[9]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[9]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Fait le plus vilain temps du monde,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[9]/#"}},"Et qu’à la fin d’Avril on couve ses tisons ?","En un moment, si vous voulez m’entendre,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[12]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[12]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ce Recit pourra vous l’apprendre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[12]/#"}},{}]},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"l":["Le Printemps accablé d’un chagrin sans pareil,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[1]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[1]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Vint un jour se plaindre au Soleil,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[1]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[2]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[2]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Et luy dit, c’est chose cruelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[2]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[3]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Que moy, qui suis dess saisons la plus belle,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[3]/#"}},"Qui fais naistre les fleurs &amp; les tendres amours,",{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[5]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Et qui par là devrois régner toûjours,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[5]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[6]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Je sois réduit, si j’ay quelque durée,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[6]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[7]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[7]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"A l’avoir si fort resserrée,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[7]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[8]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[8]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Que l’on n’a presque pas le temps","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[8]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[9]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[9]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"De reconnoistre le Printemps.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[9]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[10]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[10]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Par quelle étrange destinée","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[10]/#"}},"L'Hyver, qui des Mortels est la crainte &amp; l’effroy,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[12]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[12]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Régnera-t-il autant que moy ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[12]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[13]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[13]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ne faisant que du bien, pourquoy","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[13]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[14]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[14]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"N'ay-je que le quart de l’année ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[14]/#"}},"Encore si chacun vivoit content du sien,","Que mes Soeurs sur mon quart ne prétendissent rien,","Je n’en aurois jamais demandé davantage ;",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[18]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[18]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Mais helas ! c’est grande pitié,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[18]/#"}},"Parce que je suis doux, on me pille, on m’outrage,","Et de trois pauvres mois qui font tout mon partage,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[21]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[21]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Je n’en ay jamais la moitié.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[21]/#"}},"À peine par mes soins ranimant la Nature,","Ay-je aux Champs comme aux Bois ramené la verdure,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[24]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[24]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Qu'on voit l’Hyver fier &amp; mutin","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[24]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[25]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[25]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Venir souvent un beau matin","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[25]/#"}},"Ramenant avec luy sa maudite froidure,","Geler &amp; fleurs &amp; fruits, &amp; rendre impunément","Des pauvres Jardiniers les espérances vaines,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[29]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[29]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Enfin détruire en un moment","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[29]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[30]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[30]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ce que j’ay fait en six semaines.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[30]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[31]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[31]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Je ne suis guére mieux traité","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[31]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[32]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[32]/seg[1]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[32]/seg[2]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[32]/seg[3]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Par l’Eté.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[32]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[33]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[33]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ses ardeurs démesurées","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[33]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[34]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[34]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Sont toûjours prématurées,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[34]/#"}},"Il met à sec mes gazoüillans ruisseaux,",{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[36]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Fait taire les petits Oyseaux,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[36]/#"}},"Et vient secher mes fleurs avec tant d’insolence,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[38]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[38]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Qu'il me fait perdre patience.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[38]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[39]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[39]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ainsi parla le Printemps éperdu,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[39]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[40]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[40]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Demandant qu’il luy fust pourveu ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[40]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[41]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[41]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ce faisant que l’on fist défense","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[41]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[42]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[42]/seg[1]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[42]/seg[2]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"A l’Hyver pour l’avenir,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[42]/#"}},"Apres son temps passé, d’oser plus revenir,","De mesme qu’à l’Eté d’échauffer par avance.","Mais par malheur le Dieu qui préside aux Saisons",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[46]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[46]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ne gousta pas fort ses raisons,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[46]/#"}},"Et du pauvre Printemps la harangue inutile",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[48]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[48]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Fit aussi peu d’impression,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[48]/#"}},"Que s’il eust exhorté le Maire d’une Ville",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[50]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[50]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"A faire une Imposition.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[50]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[51]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Il eut beau dire, il eut beau faire,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[51]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[52]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[52]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Tout alla comme à l’ordinaire.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[52]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[53]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[53]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Pour se vanger de ce cruel refus","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[53]/#"}},"Il jura hautement qu’on ne le verroit plus,","Qu'il renonçoit au soin de la saison nouvelle,","Que l’Hyver reglast tout au gré de sa cervelle,","Pour luy, que jamais rien ne pourroit l’émouvoir,","Et que quand il pleuvroit, il laisseroit pleuvoir.",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[59]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[59]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Qu'il avoit un moyen facile","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[59]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[60]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"De s’assurer un agreable azile","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[60]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[61]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[61]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Qui luy feroit en seúreté","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[61]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[62]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[62]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Braver &amp; l’Hyver &amp; l’Eté.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[62]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[63]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[63]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Alors sans tarder davantage,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[63]/#"}},"Il vint se retirer dessus vostre visage ;","C'est là qu’il nous fait voir ses plus belles couleurs,","Et qu’il fait tous les jours éclore mille fleurs.","Il ne peut estre mieux, &amp; ma foy, s’il est sage,","Il n’en partira point d’une centaine d’ans ;","Il ne craint en ce lieu ny le vent, ny l’orage,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[70]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[70]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ny les injures du temps.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[70]/#"}},"D'ailleurs il gagne tout, changeant de destinée,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[72]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[72]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Puis qu’au lieu de trois mois","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[72]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[73]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[73]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Qu'il avoit à peine autrefois,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[73]/#"}},"Son régne aupres de vous dure toute l’année."]}]}}}